QuickLook DDS Plugin
====================

This is a plugin for QuickLook and Spotlight on OSX 10.5 (Intel) and later.
It allows Finder to display thumbnails and previews of DDS files, and allows
Spotlight to index DDS files by size and compression type.

Version 1.10: http://marginal.org.uk/QLdds_110.pkg

Acknowledgements
----------------
Uses the SOIL library to decode DDS files - http://www.lonesock.net/soil.html
Nyx0uf for the idea of adding image dimensions to the preview title - http://www.cocoaintheshell.com/2012/02/quicklook-images-dimensions/

